                    <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="part" n="I">
                        <ab>
                          <lb n="1"/><rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="treaty-making" key="polisE" ref="#gortyn"><placeName ref="#gortyn" type="ethnic">Γορτύνιοι</placeName></rs>.
                          <lb n="2"/><rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="treaty-making" key="polisE" ref="#chersonesos"><placeName ref="#chersonesos" type="ethnic">Λύττιοι οἱ πρὸς
                          <lb n="3"/>θαλάσσηι</placeName></rs>.
                          <lb n="4"/><rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="treaty-making" key="polisE" ref="#lato"><placeName ref="#lato" type="ethnic">Λάτιοι</placeName></rs>.
                          </ab>
                    </div>
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="part" n="II">
                        <ab>
                          <lb n="5"/><rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="treaty-making" key="polisE" ref="#lappa"><placeName ref="#lappa" type="ethnic">Λαππαῖ<surplus>ι</surplus>οι</placeName></rs>.
                          <lb n="6"/><rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="treaty-making" key="polisE" ref="#sybrita"><placeName ref="#sybrita" type="ethnic"><supplied reason="lost">Σ</supplied>υβρίτ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>οι</placeName></rs>.
                          <lb n="7"/><rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="treaty-making" key="polisE" ref="#lyttos"><placeName ref="#lyttos" type="ethnic">Λ<supplied reason="lost">ύ</supplied>ττιοι οἱ ἄν<supplied reason="lost">ω</supplied></placeName></rs>.
                          <lb n="7a"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
                          </ab>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="commentary">
                        <p>Il blocco conserva una lista di nomi di città che paiono aver stipulato accordi con Andros (verosimilmente relativi alla concessione dell’<foreign>asylia</foreign> a quest’ultima; cf. <bibl><ref target="#bib308">Rigsby, <title>Asylia</title></ref>, p. 589</bibl>), fra le quali figurano le <foreign>poleis</foreign> cretesi di Gortyna, Chersonesos (detta «Lyttos sul mare» in nome della <foreign>sympoliteia</foreign> vigente fra le due città; cf. <bibl><ref target="#bib15">Chaniotis, <title>Verträge</title></ref> 73</bibl>), Lato, Lappa, Sybrita e Lyttos.</p>
                <p><emph>Elementi istituzionali o altri termini rilevanti</emph>: <ref type="inst" target="#polis"><foreign>polis</foreign></ref><hi rend="superscript">e</hi>.</p>
                    </div>
